\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} nx^n
\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{n}{3^n}
x = 1/3
|x| <1
   \sum_{n=1}^\infty n x^n  = x \sum_{n=1}^\infty n x^{n-1}  = x \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{d}{dx} x^n = x \frac{d}{dx} \sum_{n=1}^\infty x^n = x \frac{d}{dx} \frac{x}{1-x} = \frac{x }{(1-x)^2}. 
1/(1-x) = \sum_{n=0}^\infty x^n
x = 1/3
